# Blockchain Wallet Application

A secure and user-friendly cryptocurrency wallet application for managing digital assets on the blockchain.

## Features

- Create and manage multiple cryptocurrency wallets
- Send and receive cryptocurrency transactions
- View real-time balance and transaction history
- Support for multiple cryptocurrencies (BTC, ETH, etc.)
- Secure key storage and encryption
- QR code support for easy address sharing

## Main Menu

1. Create Wallet
2. Load Wallet
3. Send Funds
4. Receive Funds
5. Check Balance
6. Transaction History
7. Settings
8. Exit

## Installation

1. Clone the repository
```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/blockchain-wallet.git
```

2. Install dependencies
```bash
cd blockchain-wallet
npm install
```

3. Configure environment variables
```bash
cp .env.example .env
# Edit .env with your settings
```

4. Start the application
```bash
npm start
```

